\define wikipediaLink(articleName)
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/$articleName$
\end

!! Wikify Wikipedia Link (Ex:WikifyWikipediaLink)

Without wikify (transclusion renders but not as part of link):

<$transclude $variable="wikipediaLink" articleName="TiddlyWiki"/>

With wikify:

<$wikify name="article" text="TiddlyWiki">
  <$transclude $variable="wikipediaLink" articleName=<<article>>/>
</$wikify>
